00:51:30.590 --> 00:51:33.970
on specific policy issues.

00:51:33.970 --> 00:51:35.690
For example, the
issue of should we

00:51:35.690 --> 00:51:37.440
be rebuilding our ICBM force?

00:51:37.440 --> 00:51:40.560
That's a very concrete,
specific issue.

00:51:40.560 --> 00:51:43.560
And you can build up
quite a head of steam

00:51:43.560 --> 00:51:49.357
in trying to slow
that process down,

00:51:49.357 --> 00:51:51.190
if you get enough people
concerned about it,

00:51:51.190 --> 00:51:54.800
and talking about
it, and debating it.

00:51:54.800 --> 00:51:56.890
But it takes masses of people.

00:51:56.890 --> 00:51:59.507
It can't be done with
