00:52:11.190 --> 00:52:17.050
about these problems, but
you also must have conviction

00:52:17.050 --> 00:52:19.067
that this is a serious problem.

00:52:19.067 --> 00:52:20.525
Not only your future
depends on it,

00:52:20.525 --> 00:52:22.720
but your children's
future depends upon it,

00:52:22.720 --> 00:52:24.950
if you want to do
something about it.

00:52:24.950 --> 00:52:27.890
I want to end on my
comment here by giving you

00:52:27.890 --> 00:52:33.520
a quote from the Irish poet
WB-- William Butler Yates,

00:52:33.520 --> 00:52:36.384
who said something very
meaningful on this problem.

00:52:36.384 --> 00:52:39.860
I'll just quote it
for you exactly.

00:52:39.860 --> 00:52:49.060
He said, "the best lack
conviction, while the worst are

00:52:49.060 --> 00:52:52.355
full of passionate intensity."

00:52:52.355 --> 00:52:54.730
And that's what I see when I
look out in the world today.

00:52:54.730 --> 00:52:59.730
I see people ranting and raving
passionately about how vital

00:52:59.730 --> 00:53:02.659
it is to be rebuilding all
of our ICBMs and so on,

00:53:02.659 --> 00:53:04.950
and the rest, well, you saw
it in the picture up there.

00:53:04.950 --> 00:53:07.480
What can I do?

00:53:07.480 --> 00:53:09.620
That's not a sufficient answer.

00:53:09.620 --> 00:53:12.710
If you have the conviction,
you educate yourself.

00:53:12.710 --> 00:53:14.370
You help educate other people.

00:53:14.370 --> 00:53:16.600
You associate yourself with
a group, like our group,

00:53:16.600 --> 00:53:19.790
for example, that is actually
working on the problem,

00:53:19.790 --> 00:53:21.520
and help them do it.

00:53:21.520 --> 00:53:25.450
There are things you can
do, if you, first of all,

00:53:25.450 --> 00:53:27.990
get the conviction that you
should be doing something,

00:53:27.990 --> 00:53:30.070
and then take the time
to educate yourself

00:53:30.070 --> 00:53:32.660
on what the real issues are.

